Metadata.Title: The Missionary of Murder
Metadata.Description: 47 has joined the Cult of Five! Hooray! The cult is sending you on your missionary to find five souls to be saved from this mortal plane! Dawn your ceremonial robe, grab your knife, and get to sacrificing! Three must be claimed by a knife, one must be killed by your holy hands and another must die by a 9mm.  Good luck on your mission, 47!
